Image-Tagger
------------

Application to fast browse, categorize and tag images.

Author: MaKraus & Contributors

Using Mono, C#, WinForms, MSBuild 2010 Project

Read more at http://linuxunddotnet.wordpress.com/ (German)
Follow MaKraus on Twitter: https://twitter.com/#!/TheMaKraus
Source & Binaries: https://github.com/MaKraus/Image-Tagger/

---
Binaries:
---

The /Releases folder does contain binaries for all stable releases.
The folder Image-Tagger-WinForms/Image-Tagger-WinForms/bin/Debug/ does contain
the most recent development build for the selected branch.

---
Configuration file:
---

On Linux systems the configuration file will be saved as ~/.config/Image-Tagger/Image-Tagger.config,
where ~/.config/ is configured as "AppData" directory. ~ is a shortcut for users home directory.

